{"text_id":205394,"tokens":["How"," to"," Make"," a"," Business"," Plan"," (","for"," Kids",")","\n\n","Are"," you"," a"," kid"," with"," a"," great"," business"," idea","?"," Do"," you"," want"," to"," turn"," your"," idea"," into"," a"," real"," business","?"," Writing"," a"," business"," plan"," is"," a"," great"," way"," to"," get"," started","!"," A"," business"," plan"," is"," a"," roadmap"," that"," helps"," you"," plan"," and"," organize"," your"," business","."," It","'","s"," like"," a"," blueprint"," for"," your"," company","."," In"," this"," article",","," we","'","ll"," show"," you"," how"," to"," make"," a"," business"," plan"," that"," will"," help"," you"," achieve"," your"," business"," goals",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1",":"," Decide"," to"," Write"," a"," Business"," Plan","**","\n","The"," first"," step"," in"," making"," a"," business"," plan"," is"," to"," decide"," that"," you"," need"," one","."," This"," might"," seem"," obvious",","," but"," it","'","s"," an"," important"," step","!"," Writing"," a"," business"," plan"," takes"," time"," and"," effort",","," but"," it","'","s"," worth"," it"," in"," the"," end","."," A"," business"," plan"," will"," help"," you"," clarify"," your"," ideas",","," make"," good"," decisions",","," and"," stay"," focused"," on"," your"," goals",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","2",":"," Write"," Down"," All"," of"," Your"," Possible"," Business"," Ideas","**","\n","Once"," you","'","ve"," decided"," to"," write"," a"," business"," plan",","," it","'","s"," time"," to"," brainstorm","!"," Write"," down"," all"," of"," your"," possible"," business"," ideas","."," Don","'","t"," worry"," too"," much"," about"," whether"," they","'","re"," good"," or"," bad"," at"," this"," point"," -"," just"," focus"," on"," getting"," all"," of"," your"," ideas"," down"," on"," paper","."," Ask"," yourself"," questions"," like",":","\n\n","*"," What"," am"," I"," good"," at","?","\n","*"," What"," do"," I"," love"," to"," do","?","