ess"," Idea"," and"," Goals","**","\n","Write"," a"," short"," paragraph"," that"," describes"," your"," business"," idea"," and"," goals","."," This"," paragraph"," should"," summarize"," what"," your"," business"," does",","," what"," products"," or"," services"," you"," offer",","," and"," what"," you"," hope"," to"," achieve","."," This"," paragraph"," will"," be"," the"," foundation"," of"," your"," business"," plan",","," so"," make"," sure"," it","'","s"," clear"," and"," concise",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","7",":"," Figure"," Out"," if"," You","'","ll"," Need"," Employees","**","\n","In"," most"," cases",","," you","'","ll"," probably"," be"," running"," your"," business"," by"," yourself",","," at"," least"," in"," the"," beginning","."," But"," it","'","s"," still"," important"," to"," think"," about"," whether"," you","'","ll"," need"," employees"," in"," the"," future","."," Will"," you"," need"," help"," with"," tasks"," like"," manufacturing",","," marketing",","," or"," customer"," service","?"," Make"," a"," list"," of"," the"," tasks"," that"," you","'","ll"," need"," help"," with"," and"," think"," about"," how"," you","'","ll"," find"," employees"," to"," help"," you",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","8",":"," Make"," a"," List"," of"," Any"," Supplies"," You"," Will"," Need"," to"," Get"," Started","**","\n","Make"," a"," list"," of"," the"," supplies"," you","'","ll"," need"," to"," get"," started","."," This"," might"," include"," things"," like"," materials",","," equipment",","," and"," office"," supplies","."," Think"," about"," what"," you","'","ll"," need"," to"," make"," your"," product"," or"," offer"," your"," service",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","9",":"," List"," the"," Ongoing"," Expenses"," You"," Expect"," to"," Have","**","\n","Make"," a"," list"," of"," the"," ongoing"," expenses"," you"," expect"," to"," have","."," This"," might"," include"," things"," like"," rent",","," utilities",","," and"," marketing"," expenses","."," Think"," about"," how"," you","'","ll"," pay"," for"," these"," expenses"," and"," how"," they","'","ll"," affect"," your"," business",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","0",":"," Decide"," What"," You"," Will"," Be"," Charging"," for"," Your"," Product","/","Service","**","\n","Decide"," what"," you","'","ll"," be"," charging"," for"," your"," product"," or"," service","."," Think"," about"," how"," much"," it"," costs"," for"," you"," to"," make"," your"," product"," or"," perform"," your"," service","."," You","'","ll"," need"," to"," charge"," enough"," to"," cover"," your"," costs"," and"," make"," a"," profit",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","1",":"," Figure"," Out"," Who"," Your"," Customers"," Are","**","\n","Write"," down"," all"," of"," the"," different"," types"," of"," customers"," who"," you"," think"," will"," want"," your"," product"," or"," service","."," Think"," about"," what"," they"," need"," and"," want",","," and"," how"," you"," can"," meet"," those"," needs",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","2",":"," Figure"," Out"," if"," You"," Have"," Any"," Competitors","**","\n","Research"," your"," competition","."," Find"," out"," who"," else"," is"," offering"," products"," or"," services"," like"," yours","."," Think"," about"," how"," you"," can"," differentiate"," yourself"," from"," them"," and"," offer"," something"," unique",".","\n\n","**","Step"," ","1","3",":"," Explore"," Your"," Marketing"," Strategy"," Options","**","\n","Think"," about"," how"," you","'","ll"," market"," your"," business","."," Will"," you"," use"," social"," media",","," advertising",","," or"],"sub_source":"wikihow","model":"llama3-70b","label":1}